# Node Anonymity — Research & Architecture for Zephyria

## Threat Model: What We're Defending Against

An adversary wants to answer: **"Which physical node originated transaction X?"**

Attack vectors on Zephyria's current P2P stack:

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Adversary Goals] --> B[Link TX → Originating Node IP]
    A --> C[Link TX → Validator Identity]
    A --> D[Link Node → Geographic Location]
    A --> E[Fingerprint Node by Behavior]
    
    B --> B1[First-seen Timing Analysis]
    B --> B2[Source IP in UDP Packets]
    B --> B3[Gulf Stream Direct Forwarding]
    
    C --> C1[Validator Address in ENR]
    C --> C2[BLS Pubkey in Peer Handshake]
    C --> C3[Shred Producer Signature]
    
    D --> D1[IP Geolocation]
    D --> D2[Latency Triangulation]
    
    E --> E1[TX Submission Patterns]
    E --> E2[Unique Subnet Subscriptions]
    E --> E3[Message Ordering Fingerprint]
```

---

## Current Leakage Points in Zephyria

| Component | File | What's Leaked | Severity |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Peer Identity** | [peer.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/peer.zig) | `ip`, `validator_address`, `bls_pubkey`, `id` stored per peer | 🔴 Critical |
| **Discovery (ENR)** | [discovery.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/discovery.zig) | `pubkey`, `ip4`, `validator_addr`, `stake` broadcast to all | 🔴 Critical |
| **Gulf Stream** | [gulf_stream.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/gulf_stream.zig) | TXs forwarded directly to predicted leader → leader knows who sent | 🟡 High |
| **Turbine** | [turbine.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/turbine.zig) | `producer_signature` in shreds, tree topology reveals layer position | 🟡 High |
| **Server** | [server.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/server.zig) | UDP `recvfrom` captures source IP of every packet | 🔴 Critical |
| **Auth Message** | [types.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/types.zig) | `AuthMsg` contains `public_key` and `signature` | 🟡 High |
| **Subnet Assignment** | [types.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/src/p2p/types.zig) | Deterministic from node identity → narrows anonymity set | 🟠 Medium |

